<plot>What is the definition of art? Who defines it? In the world of modern and contemporary art, art critics, artists, and art admirers repetitively tackle these questions without mercy. Reclusive and tiresome of the monotonous world outside his home, Sid Dixon is a well-known abstract artist whose work is tirelessly revered by a wide fan-base. Yet upon receiving something much different from his usual fan letters, Dixon is thrown into a predicament in which he must defend his art, as well as the right to call his work his own.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?076248</url></doc>
